{{#> layout}}
  <div class="notification-banner">
    <div class="banner-icon">ðŸ“Š</div>
    <h1 class="banner-title">Margin Statement Available</h1>
    <p class="banner-subtitle">For period ending {{formatDate statementEndDate 'short'}}</p>
  </div>

  <p>Dear <strong>{{clientName}}</strong>,</p>

  <p>Your margin statement for the period <strong>{{formatDate statementStartDate 'short'}}</strong> to <strong>{{formatDate statementEndDate 'short'}}</strong> is now available. This statement provides a detailed overview of your margin utilization, pledged securities, and available trading power.</p>

  <div class="statement-details">
    <h3 class="detail-title">Statement Details</h3>
    
    <div class="detail-row">
      <div class="detail-label">Client ID</div>
      <div class="detail-value">{{clientId}}</div>
    </div>
    <div class="detail-row">
      <div class="detail-label">Statement Period</div>
      <div class="detail-value">{{statementPeriod}}</div>
    </div>
    <div class="detail-row">
      <div class="detail-label">Statement Date</div>
      <div class="detail-value">{{formatDate statementDate 'short'}}</div>
    </div>
    <div class="detail-row">
      <div class="detail-label">Account Type</div>
      <div class="detail-value">{{accountType}}</div>
    </div>
    <div class="detail-row">
      <div class="detail-label">Segment</div>
      <div class="detail-value">{{segment}}</div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="margin-summary">
    <h3 class="margin-summary-title">Margin Summary</h3>
    
    <div class="summary-row">
      <div class="summary-label">Cash Balance</div>
      <div class="summary-value">{{formatCurrency cashBalance 'INR'}}</div>
    </div>
    
    <div class="summary-row">
      <div class="summary-label">Collateral Value</div>
      <div class="summary-value">{{formatCurrency collateralValue 'INR'}}</div>
    </div>
    
    <div class="summary-row">
      <div class="summary-label">Total Margin Available</div>
      <div class="summary-value positive">{{formatCurrency totalMarginAvailable 'INR'}}</div>
    </div>
    
    <div class="summary-row">
      <div class="summary-label">Margin Utilized</div>
      <div class="summary-value {{marginUtilizedClass}}">{{formatCurrency marginUtilized 'INR'}}</div>
    </div>
    
    <div class="summary-row">
      <div class="summary-label">Available Margin</div>
      <div class="summary-value {{availableMarginClass}}">{{formatCurrency availableMargin 'INR'}}</div>
    </div>
    
    <div class="summary-row">
      <div class="summary-label">Margin Utilization</div>
      <div class="summary-value {{marginUtilizationClass}}">{{marginUtilization}}%</div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <p>The detailed margin statement includes a breakdown of your margin utilization by segment, pledged securities, and margin requirements for each open position. You can view and download the complete statement by clicking the button below.</p>

  <div class="cta-container">
    <a href="{{statementDownloadUrl}}" class="button">DOWNLOAD STATEMENT</a>
  </div>

  <div class="note-box">
    <div class="note-icon">ðŸ’¡</div>
    <div class="note-content">
      <p style="margin-bottom: 8px;"><strong>Need Help Understanding Your Statement?</strong></p>
      <p style="margin-bottom: 0;">Our support team is available to help you understand your margin statement. Contact us at <strong>{{supportEmail}}</strong> or call <strong>{{supportPhone}}</strong>.</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <p style="text-align: center; margin-top: 32px; font-style: italic;">
    This is an automated statement notification. Please do not reply to this email.
  </p>
{{/layout}}